hes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aEurasiaxHistoryvCongresses. 0aEurasiaxRelationsvCongresses. 4aAsian Studies. 4aCultural Studies. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / World / Asian.2bisacsh  aTransnational History, History of Art, Museums, Heritage, Decolonization.1 aChatterjee, Indrani, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChu, Cindy Yik-yi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGermer, Andrea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKhullar, Sonal, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKikuchi, Yoshiyuki, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKikuchi, Yoshiyuki, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMulgund, Deepti, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPieris, Anoma, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aShin, Boram, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStolte, Carolien, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStolte, Carolien, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWang, Shu-Li, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aČapková, Helena, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package 2016-2018z978311066731808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package Backlist 2015-2017z978311060644708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311066284908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAsian Studies Contemporary Collection eBook Packagez978311064982640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048527472zCo-access DOI 